{"tid":744498,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"荷李活火速搶拍電影版鬧雙胞胎","createTime":"2018-07-16T03:37:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T08:25:21.000Z","uid":160973,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fc9dba9d2998ad7e64fb04a5bff9c2df0fa43927","tid":744498,"uid":160973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T03:37:23.000Z","msg":"泰國「野豬」足球隊12名少年和教練被困洞穴一事舉世矚目，就在歷時17日、逾千人參與的搜救行動正式結束後，馬上有荷李活電影公司宣布開拍電影版，還要不只牽涉一間片商，而是有兩間搶拍！<br />\n<br />\n荷李活一向鍾情真人真事改編的災難題材，如占士法蘭高(James Franco)主演的《127小時》及改編智利金礦礦工被困的《絕地拯救33》，而早在泰國少足拯救行動仍在進行時，已有不少網友戲言，荷李活絕會不放過這樣的矚目事件，更很大可能會邀請如狄維莊遜(Dwayne Johnson)等大隻佬上演一個救十個的英雄故事等云云。<br />\n<br />\n不出他們所料，在行動結束不久後，專拍福音電影的Pure Flix Entertainment火速宣布開拍電影版，除了公司創辦人之一Michael Scott早在拯救行動中身處山洞附近，協助救援工作亦跟潛水員作訪談，率先蒐集第一手資料，如今更派出多位人員到泰北為拍片作初步訪問，並考慮將故事主線圍繞兩名首先發現少年的英藉潛水員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2NkcZK5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2NkcZK5&d=YANgR46M55LsrvAyiDZ4JkjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=35f40550\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2NkcZK5</a>"},{"pid":"b7811fcf81221b17350525d3c6a13632fc46fde9","tid":744498,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T05:02:59.000Z","msg":"The rock <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75ed42596c232da2ff3be1a49153f1bff28bb856","tid":744498,"uid":28800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T05:04:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe738f83b43e214ceb51a938fc47a70ffce6add8","tid":744498,"uid":22913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7811fcf81221b17350525d3c6a13632fc46fde9","tid":744498,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T05:02:59.000Z","msg":"The rock <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 